    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The library `algolia-frontend-components` requires a Docsearch configuration (`new alg.communityHeader(docSearch)`) otherwise it throws.\r\n\r\nIt should not be possible to interact with Docsearch though (and that's a temporary website).\r\n\r\nI checked on the Vue InstantSearch v2 website and it seems like it's not disabled either.",
